Module com.example.breakout_clone
Package com.example.breakout_clone.controller.game

Class GameEndController

java.lang.Object
com.example.breakout_clone.controller.game.GameEndController
public class GameEndController extends Object
Controller class for the GameOverView and the GameCompleteView. It is responsible for handling the user inputs and creating the binding between the model and view.
Author:
Praket Chavan
See Also:
GameModel
